trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeNodeStyle"></xref> objects that is in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeNodeStyle"> </xref> objekter som er i en <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The TreeNodeStyleCollection class is used to store and manage a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeNodeStyle> objects.
trans-unit.target: Klassen TreeNodeStyleCollection brukes til å lagre og behandle en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeNodeStyle>objekter.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeNodeStyle>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView.LevelStyles%2A> property, of type TreeNodeStyleCollection, stores the node styles for the individual levels of a tree.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView.LevelStyles%2A>egenskap av typen TreeNodeStyleCollection, lagrer node-stiler for individuelle nivåer i et tre.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView.LevelStyles%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView.LevelStyles%2A> property is an alternative to the individual style properties, such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView.NodeStyle%2A> property, that control node styles at different levels of the tree.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView.LevelStyles%2A>egenskapen er et alternativ til individuelle stilegenskaper som den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView.NodeStyle%2A>egenskapen som kontrollerer noden stiler på ulike nivåer i treet.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView.NodeStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView.LevelStyles%2A>

trans-unit.source: The first style in the collection corresponds to the node style in the first level of the tree.
trans-unit.target: Den første malen i samlingen tilsvarer stilen node i det første nivået i treet.

trans-unit.source: The second style in the collection corresponds to the node style in the second level of the tree, and so on.
trans-unit.target: Andre stilen i samlingen tilsvarer stilen node i nivå på tre og så videre.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView.LevelStyles%2A> property is most often used to generate table of contents–style navigation menus where nodes at a certain level should have the same appearance, regardless of whether they have child nodes.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView.LevelStyles%2A>egenskapen brukes vanligvis til å generere tabellen med innholdet – stilen navigasjonsmenyer der noder på et bestemt nivå må ha samme utseendet, uavhengig om de har underordnede noder.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView.LevelStyles%2A>

trans-unit.source: The TreeNodeStyleCollection class inherits most of its members from the <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: TreeNodeStyleCollection klassen arver de fleste av medlemmene fra <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>klasse.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>

trans-unit.source: For more information about the inherited members, see <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om arvede medlemmer, kan du se <xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.StateManagedCollection>
